    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should probably see a doctor but honestly i'm just too busy right now. i've seen some wellness influencers saying that mega-dosing for a short period is actually a standard way to fix a deficiency without waiting for blood tests. if i only do it for like 10 or 14 days, won't my body just absorb what it needs and the rest will be fine? i just want to get my energy back asap.",
